起始；突然出现；突然跳起；突然涌出；

sent.orig: Arlo Belshee's team worked in a start-up, where frequent, entrepreneurial shifts in direction are commonplace.
sent.trans: ArloBelshee的团队致力于start-up,在start-up时，企业方向性改变非常频繁。

sent.orig: Click the start button, point to settings, and then click control panel.
sent.trans: 单击开始(Start)按钮，指向设置(Settingd)项，然后单击控制面板(Control Panel)。

sent.orig: Begin at START. You can move horizontally and vertically, but not diagonally.
sent.trans: 由START开始，你只可以横向、纵向移动，但不可以交叉走。

sent.orig: You can simply use the start_t type above as-is.
sent.trans: 你可以如上只使用start_t类型。

sent.orig: Please reconnect the controller and press START to continue.
sent.trans: 请重新接上控制器然后按下[START]来继续游戏。
